Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:08.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}空梦一场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}宿于右手的空虚记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:15.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}于无人知晓的世界尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:20.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}被无尽的雨水打湿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:26.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}守护想要守护之物的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:31.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}无法相信这一切的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:36.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}接受一切 探求明日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:39.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}勇敢之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:44.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}伸出手去你会见到光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:50.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}遍体伤痕的你会看到我的光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:54.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}于高举的剑尖处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}将思绪交织
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:04.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}心愿超越时空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:09.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你的勇敢之光
