Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.39,0:25:49.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如果心终会消失不再
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.02,0:25:53.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}至少纵声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.06,0:26:05.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恸哭和绝望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.78,0:26:11.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}等待我们的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.66,0:26:18.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}都不过是生命梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.67,0:26:21.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为之奋斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.55,0:26:26.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}当下的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.89,0:26:32.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你哭泣的夜晚之中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.02,0:26:39.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏有遥远未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.32,0:26:43.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静谧在等待你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.99,0:26:49.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}耀眼的丘陵 必能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.12,0:26:55.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你所在的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.83,0:27:01.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}奏响你的心铃
